'''Keschel''' was a rare mineral found on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Tyne's Horky]]. A majority of the planet's financial stability was based upon the success of Keschel miners such as [[Kleb Zellock]], [[Jann Tosh]] and his uncle, [[Putch Gundarian|Gundy]]. The value of Keschel ore was represented in the form of currency known as a [[Keshel]].<ref name="TLP">{{DroidsCite|The Lost Prince}}</ref>

